tems）</li>	<li>市场营销（Marketing）</li>	<li>市场、公共政策与法律（Markets, Public Policy &amp; Law）</li>	<li>运营与技术管理（Operations &amp; Technology Management）</li>	<li>组织行为（Organizational Behavior）</li>	<li>战略与创新（Strategy &amp; Innovation）*(1)</li></ul><p><strong>研究机构</strong></p><p>商学院设有以下实验室和研究中心，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>行为实验室（Behavioral Lab）</li>	<li>团队学习中心（Center for Team Learning (CTL)）</li>	<li>中高管理层圆桌会议（Executive Development Roundtable (EDRT)）</li>	<li>公共政策研究所（Health Policy Institute (HPI)）</li>	<li>人力资源政策研究所（Human Resources Policy Institute (HRPI)）</li>	<li>国际工作研究所（Institute for Global Work (IGW)）</li>	<li>非盈利机构与领导研究所（Institute for Nonprofit Management &amp; Leadership (INML)）</li>	<li>技术企业学与商业化研究所（Institute for Technology Entrepreneurship and Commercialization (ITEC)）*(2)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>商学院教员列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=KruBHNWOktZGdUxpKKKKKKRg30RPnWZBHwHw19Uwu9hv3iZtscSdsD28CvGAKrIdrQKG1l3NFbLw6xLYrE-vIxKwNjayZ5m' target='_blank'>Faculty Directory</a></li>	<li>知名教授列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=IrnDV7P1kTXJRLLZxNrvcZUvb5Ksp95_o3J1pCLTC5Vzzs799U_WrhPayNCzkGgBz0YmdMnxv8dTPsBfjlPE7UfrnhKL8QYQ-rwornRCELySsBheUoyXbam' target='_blank'>Distinguished Faculty</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=4rjT-BDdwTChv_eOvu9cjWhLch4y_eY1PVIdeWcldz71e_G-IzqQiByN-zBeYfPRmIqFEFWde38Ph_7k8kIH1FLj-1tEbP1PLmVXYYRdG0_637-8zvqf' target='_blank'>Departments</a> Questrom School of Business, Boston University</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=arBPkMlmkYo9i1YXCCCCCCymFyvZmTDgztZcZcgRluXxIJn2qDiHWg7HhUOslgK_e9X6pHJFlzC6si-Wt7ZW59jPBkfjCbNmascIur' target='_blank'>Research Centers</a> Questrom School of Business, Boston University</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>MBA项目</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:16.94%">			<p>USNEWS排名</p>			</td>			<td style="width:14.4%">			<p>42</p>		