ip）</li>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E9%87%91%E8%9E%8D' target='_blank'>金融</a>（Finance）</li>	<li>国际管理（International Management）</li>	<li>组织与领导转型（Leadership and Organizational Transformation）</li>	<li><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%B8%82%E5%9C%BA%E8%90%A5%E9%94%80' target='_blank'>市场营销</a>（Marketing）</li>	<li>运营与技术管理（Operations and Technology Management）</li>	<li>战略与商业分析（Strategy and Business Analysis）*(17)</li></ul><p>双学位项目：</p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:87px">			<p>所在学院</p>			</td>			<td style="width:193px">			<p>项目名称</p>			</td>			<td style="width:227px">			<p>项目英文名称</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td rowspan="2" style="width:87px">			<p>文理研究生院</p>			</td>			<td style="width:193px">			<p>MBA/国际关系硕士</p>			</td>			<td style="width:227px">			<p>MBA/MA in International Relations</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:193px">			<p>MBA/经济学硕士</p>			</td>			<td style="width:227px">			<p>MBA/MA in Economics</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:87px">			<p>传播学院</p>			</td>			<td style="width:193px">			<p>MBA/媒体投资硕士</p>			</td>			<td style="width:227px">			<p>MBA/MS in Media Ventures*</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td rowspan="2" style="width:87px">			<p>法学院</p>			</td>			<td style="width:193px">			<p>MBA/法学博士（法学与管理）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:227px">			<p>MBA/JD in Law and Management</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:193px">			<p>MBA/法学博士（卫生部门管理）</p>			</td>			<td style="width:227px">			<p>MBA/JD in Health Sector Management</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:87px">			<p>医学院</p>			</td>			<td style="width:193px">			<p>MBA/医学博士</p>			</td>			<td style="width:227px">			<p>MBA/MD</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td rowspan="2" style="width:87px">			<p>公共卫生学院</p>			</td>			<td style="width:193px">			<p>MBA/医疗管理公共卫生硕士</p>			</td>			<td style="width:227px">			<p>MBA/MPH in Health Care Management</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:193px">			<p>MBA/全球卫生管理公共卫生硕士</p>			</td>			<td styl