业治理（Corporate governance）</li>		<li>国际会计（International accounting）</li>		<li>医疗机构与管理控制（Management control in health care organizations）*(7)&nbsp;</li>	</ul>	</li>	<li>信息系统（Information Systems）	<ul>		<li>市场与机构应急网络形式（Emergent Network forms of markets and organizations）</li>		<li>新技术与组织能力（Organizational Capability through new technologies）</li>		<li>IT投资（Investing in IT）*(8)&nbsp;</li>	</ul>	</li>	<li>市场营销（Marketing）&nbsp;</li>	<li>运营与技术管理（Operations &amp; Technology Management）	<ul>		<li>物流管理（Supply chain management）</li>		<li>产品开发管理（Product development management）</li>		<li>卫生服务管理（Health service management）*(9)</li>	</ul>	</li>	<li>组织行为（Organizational Behavior）</li>	<li>战略与创新（Strategy &amp; Innovation）	<ul>		<li>创意与设计（Creativity and design）</li>		<li>创新与新商业模式扩散（Diffusion of innovations and new business models）</li>		<li>破坏性创新与平台竞争（Disruptive innovation and platform competition）</li>		<li>行业标准动态（Dynamics of industry standards）</li>		<li>创业管理与内部创业（Entrepreneurship and intrapreneurship）</li>		<li>入门时间优势（Entry-timing advantages）</li>		<li>灵活性、模块化与企业绩效（Flexibility, modularity, and firm performance）</li>		<li>创新战略（Innovation strategies）</li>		<li>创新社区与网络（Innovation communities and networks）</li>		<li>知识产权（Intellectual property）</li>		<li>学习与知识转换（Learning and knowledge transfer）</li>		<li>重组与企业转型（Reorganization and firm turnaround）</li>		<li>战略联盟与收购（Strategic alliances and acquisitions）</li>		<li>选择性企业专长（Selected industry expertise: telecommunications, software, biotechnology, information technology, nanotechnology, creative industries）*(10)(11)</li>	</ul>	</li></ul><p><strong>费用与奖学金</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td colspan="2" style="width:250px">			<p>管理学博士</p>			</td>			<td style="width:61px">&nbsp;</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:52px">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:196px">			<p>PhD Tuition</p>			</td>			<td style="width:61px">			<p>$49,176</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:52px">			<p>杂费</p>			</