um Communication &amp; Measurement</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:19.78%">			<p>复杂生物信号处理</p>			</td>			<td style="width:30.96%">			<p>Complex BioSignal Processing</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.5%">			<p>无线电通信与等离子体研究</p>			</td>			<td style="width:30.76%">			<p>Radio Communications and Plasma Research</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:19.78%">			<p>离散事件系统控制</p>			</td>			<td style="width:30.96%">			<p>Control of Discrete Event Systems</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.5%">			<p>半导体光子学</p>			</td>			<td style="width:30.76%">			<p>Semiconductor Photonics</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:19.78%">			<p>多维信号处理</p>			</td>			<td style="width:30.96%">			<p>Multi-Dimensional Signal Processing</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.5%">			<p>宽带隙半导体</p>			</td>			<td style="width:30.76%">			<p>Wide Band Gap Semiconductors</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:19.78%">			<p>多媒体通信</p>			</td>			<td style="width:30.96%">			<p>Multimedia Communications</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.5%">&nbsp;</td>			<td style="width:30.76%">&nbsp;</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:19.78%">			<p>网络优化与控制</p>			</td>			<td style="width:30.96%">			<p>Network Optimization and Control</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.5%">&nbsp;</td>			<td style="width:30.76%">&nbsp;</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:19.78%">			<p>网络与信息系统</p>			</td>			<td style="width:30.96%">			<p>Networking and Information Systems</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.5%">&nbsp;</td>			<td style="width:30.76%">&nbsp;</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:19.78%">			<p>视觉信息处理</p>			</td>			<td style="width:30.96%">			<p>Visual Information Processing</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.5%">&nbsp;</td>			<td style="width:30.76%">&nbsp;</td>		</tr>	</tbody></table><p>*(16)</p><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>教员列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=KruBHNWYkmG0lavZ999999aIyR95wG73AUBaBauODXuK8zUpmiBTZhPxAfPh6iD2lT_vAFY3S0LsOZje' target='_blank'>Faculty</a></li>	<li>工程学院硕士项目FAQ：<a rel=