></p><p>波士顿大学材料科学与工程学部（Division of Materials Science &amp; Engineering (MSE)）研究生阶段开设有以下学位项目，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>材料科学与工程硕士（M.Eng in Materials Science &amp; Engineering）：为期1年，共计32个学分，不要求撰写论文，如选择实习项目，2年以内可获得此学位*(5)</li>	<li>材料科学与工程理学硕士（MS in Materials Science &amp; Engineering）：为期1年，共计32个学分，但该项目学生需撰写论文，因此为期1-2年*(6)</li>	<li>材料科学与工程博士（PhD in Materials Science &amp; Engineering）：设有&ldquo;Post-BS PhD&rdquo;和&ldquo;Post-MS PhD&rdquo;两种课程设置，也就是说已拥有学士说硕士学位的学生均可申请*(7)(8)</li></ul><p>注：上述项目要求申请者具备理工科专业背景。</p><p><strong>研究领域</strong></p><p>材料科学与工程学部有以下研究领域，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>生物材料（Biomaterials）</li>	<li>电子与光学材料（Electronic and photonic materials）</li>	<li>能源与环境材料（Materials for energy and environment）</li>	<li>纳米材料（Nanomaterials）*(9)</li></ul><p>此外，该系开设的研究实验室有：</p><ul>	<li>Advanced Materials Process Control Laboratory</li>	<li>Applied Electromagnetics</li>	<li>Atomic Membrane Lab</li>	<li>Biomimetics Materials Engineering Laboratory</li>	<li>Cell and Tissue Mechanics Laboratory</li>	<li>Coker Group</li>	<li>Collins Laboratory</li>	<li>Computational Electronics Laboratory</li>	<li>Computational Energy Laboratory</li>	<li>Dennis Lab</li>	<li>Doerrer Group</li>	<li>FemtoSpec Laboratory</li>	<li>Green Manufacturing Laboratory</li>	<li>High-Temperature Chemical and Electrochemical Processing of Materials Laboratory</li>	<li>High Temperature Oxidation Laboratory</li>	<li>Integrated Photonics Laboratory (IPL)</li>	<li>Interfacial Fluid Dynamics Laboratory</li>	<li>Lab for Engineering Education &amp; Development (LEED)</li>	<li>Laboratory for Diagnostics and Global Healthcare Technologies</li>	<li>Laboratory for Microsystems Technology</li>	<li>Laboratory of Integrated Nanophotonics &amp; Biosensing Systems (LINBS)</li>	<li>Materials Theory Group</li>	<li>Materials X-Ray Diffraction Laboratory</li>	<li>Matrix Mechanotransduction Lab</li>	<li>Microscopy Laboratory</li>	<li>Multifunctional Materials Spectroscopy Laboratory</li>	<li>Multiscale Laser Lithography Laboratory (ML-cubed)</li>	<li>Multiscale Tissue Biomechanics Laboratory</li>	<li>Nano Heat Transfer Laboratory</li>	<li>Nanomedicine and Medical Acoustics Laboratory</li>	<li>Nanoscale Energy-Fluids Transport Laboratory</li>	<li>Nanoscale Mechanical Engineering Laboratory</li>	<li>Nanostructured Fibers and Nonlinear Optics Laboratory</li>	<li>Novel Materials Laboratory</li>	<li>Optical Characterization &amp; Nanophotonics Laboratory (OCN)</li>	<li>Orthopaedic &amp; Developmental Biomechanics Laboratory</li>	<li>Physical Acoustics Laboratories</li>	<li>Powder Metallurgy &amp; X-ray Laboratory</li>	<li>Precision Engineering Research (PERL) Laboratory</li>	<li>Semiconductor Photonics Research Laboratory</li>	<li>The Sharifzadeh Group</li>	<li>Solid State Research Laboratory</li>	<li>Surface Modification Laboratory</li>	<li>The Tien Group</li>	<li>Tsui Laboratory</li>	<li>Ultrafast Nanostructure Optics (UNO) Laboratory</li>	<li>Vibrations Laboratory</li>	<li>Wide Bandgap Semiconductor Laboratory*(10)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>教员列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=dr1GqV87wzOaRd8jssssssIlnkvhL-JrAiAidH6ifHI4nVJ9ms35cKZ5gKZTS0CsTYWN1ikJrvBP' target='_blank'>Faculty</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=dr1GqVpXLCZnSfcKssssss9ovmOHfTUXrm0m0gYc0IYdA7_tAFYBvoZWBUH6PKR6OU3TOS1AgSMfgK0meo8flCcvOKlY9PvzB' target='_blank'>Frequently Asked Questions Test Scores and Requirements</a> Boston University</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=orDtO5aGLmpEbhjJ66666Sx2L3YrbBXoG5G5sRm5tR9DLWX2TCKPs40DOpzP89K5Ll05O4srs41wh-kskFclSJ7mhJUFDJtTYFaLQJl4Ybn-NMIyc9Yx5uIzc2jyKmYycmjyJ2I-6R6O' target='_blank'>Estimate of Expenses for International Students</a> Boston University</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Hr3vKzNJwaAvy-zDmmmmmpt9Ns9HMRcncsO1O1kp2UsbWK5zTCdbjJqE_pQSuk617X6PDKsCHhQnM9ytToMsY5hfjE_DhX_paKLiGk0AjJdNH0dC1jrd5M3m5gWxThRO9' target='_blank'>Applicatio