stics）：PhD项目仅在计划招生的年份，招收有限人数的学生，且通常只有申请者拥有英语、其他外语、言语与语言、语言学或相关领域硕士学位，且与导师研究兴趣相一致，成绩优异的情况下才录取。如申请者未能满足上述学术要求，可先申请MA项目，待修完前置课程之后，再申请PhD项目*(5)(6)</li></ul><p>系主任将在申请者被录取后，与学生商讨是否授予RA或TA奖学金，通常大部分TA奖学金不会授予MA项目新生，但2年级或3年级是有可能，也是有机会的。如学生曾经拥有大学外语教学经历 ，可联系系主任，以争取相应的机会。*(7)</p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=FrFYCW9NLT8196J7GmKJX9--qgd0eb1twOvtigUbwtSv9nG92tv27LFTkbSwodR4Gqotd4c2wn0jwGEHpnQpJSFAGolV0ASF3zDL1-Rtdvvx8MO7qFUuNaZNKadMsh-gm3Sv0P8e1qxqcEmzoa3k-itJjbvmGra1Q' target='_blank'>Estimate of Expenses for International Students</a> Boston University</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ArAjQunMwr-KeqZyJJJJJsGke_8ACbPslXwvwv0tJpO2cLGhYZK7EOPYs3icEOgZLygaN9RJDIRTo_WOc0P1cezuq7Qe8vGqg1SrV3ifQoxJaf6JQ2y7W39GRlqlyf4g1t_fFMiYa4G-EcKtXUJeH1cmejMmTe7M2hxZeBE48hEB8PeBoQSCIkt8X' target='_blank'>Application Requirements and Deadlines</a> Applied Linguistics at Boston University</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=9rpcSXLiw8gc07Rm7MZwmxfyIzj3zDeF-Cls_-RpdHv3WGhgthGmgv1OKM1IVn2ZqsEOO9tc719shRN0vHWhPF31laO2AoBZv9EIQTXBKPBZaQnNhNfbx9AZMfrW3y' target='_blank'>How to Apply</a> Applied Linguistics at Boston University</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=WrSJLFCZLDXYcySfFFFFFFc-Pfx_DigqNy6K7GkwDdvkfQJVomXcmCwKvBjAr6BJVyBxCEOBcMpT63QA0r' target='_blank'>M.A. Program</a> Applied Linguistics at Boston University</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=brEVbyf0Lr9Df3TPxxxxxxdYGJphQcuOivf_dhRzmnRI7J6OiNEz7ouI9ZmhdZshE-1_P6UYVw4' target='_blank'>PhD Program</a> Applied Linguistics at Boston University</p><p>(6) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=lreSUwaQkrW5UySNyyyyyyYfaHR0cDovxBHwHw19UuXxIJn2qDa_4WZmsUEfaWNzL2RlqdjI5dbPoQQxHTQxj5SOKa' target='_blank'>Degree Programs</a> Applied Linguistics at Boston University</p><p>(7) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_27wzOaRdvu44