netary）</li>	<li>银河系外与宇宙学（Extragalactic &amp; Cosmology）</li>	<li>空间物理（Space Physics）</li>	<li>天文仪器（Instrumentation）*(6)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>教员列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=orDtO5ciw8gc07OgeiJkAvfFET4hlcEfY_M8JvFOF98lcEGvl1VA--OJ_s1dELUvVVnOswQd98o2Osj_4ovwYfjSAPmSIvhCA' target='_blank'>Faculty</a></li>	<li>研究生手册：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=IrnDV7Plk9aKYUGAWWWWWXXu82oW4Z0DlDU9U9-_zWqLtpR9_0Ichb5wrStlsEX_DEhQ6hgR070ZLnXWJSXWySMB1ud6nGTMpnU8p38dX9q4DnMjyEztNWwhD' target='_blank'>Graduate Student Brochure</a>(PDF)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=VrxbIdtOLi1FD4HCAAAufftenoGiaPSTBOROR-38RU34boxTnIJdy-hYbczKyu4dRo9YRch-a-O37fxLWL2pMiw0mKqP2BIPajpB0GLPy-pQ03pP4tr7VfkV5WyqgLx6MLy6gLIq5B2Z2P' target='_blank'>Estimate of Expenses for International Students</a> Boston University</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Gr-dDkOGwx30hoRg333332dfdwGzQOEt1b2c2cjQhK6WnUKFwGE6v02UJh7fFNpVeN5_MFZA0FPAjFtjXNMHwCvcEz7CEoaqlzeOg3ZsRrfTzxNpWSikOcxXH5pwEmfwkmLy3cNoKlfU29T_EuXd5WOZtdYZboHN5vOIF89boZb' target='_blank'>Graduate Program &ndash; Admission</a> Astronomy Department, Boston University</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=WrSJLFTpwOBAjWxrZQqU1x1VjjYJLoxzREBYFqtyhSCMvtOWhzGxuJqzayhWDuqf2GH1dVUB76eAhWQi381Oe1bVUt7xrMO8MEAs7dyfl6i_8x1' target='_blank'>Graduate Program &ndash; M.A. in Astronomy</a> Boston University</p><p>(4) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=nrIeztgskL3ojCtEggggggven2Gssb1_ITLTLpnPLGnYe8c_um-Kt9D2lgCnIgLpuyAC_anXGe4_w67BISoB2y4XLSJikjY9rj' target='_blank'>Ph.D. in Astronomy</a> Boston University</p><p>(5) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=7r_i3IKww36DmOLWQQQQQQ7q36iuZ2dOBH8H8KvT8wvf6JzO3CI46xtcSCIjB7rf6Hef6wQPZV1GZVqcM9LE' target='_blank'>Degree Programs</a> Graduate School of Arts &amp; Sciences, Boston University</p><p>(6) <