00。所有PhD新生可获得为期5年Fellowship奖学金。*(3)</p><p><strong>研究领域</strong></p><p>物理系有以下研究领域，分别是：</p><ul>	<li>基本粒子理论（Elementary Particle Theory）</li>	<li>基本粒子实验（Elementary Particle Experiment）</li>	<li>精密粒子实验（Precision Particle Experiment）</li>	<li>凝聚物质理论（Condensed Matter Theory）</li>	<li>统计物理（Statistical Physics）</li>	<li>凝聚物质实验（Condensed Matter Experiment）</li>	<li>计算物理（Computational Physics）</li>	<li>生物物理（Biological Physics）*(5)</li></ul><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>教员列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=kr53aG4zLo3V1tbI22222211DAUIk0fsa7iXvEt1lQ1Ctd1YadC5pI2PQsoDLP4SjhEfUBEVCBr8fQ30X-1CeF_f57cTCxdgIyjr3CBX' target='_blank'>Faculty/Lecturers</a></li>	<li>PhD项目要求：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=wrYmhlEpLBGgpjFkSSSSSSa9dVsJy8CpNZJCYzvtYH2NSHQDS-baRWI-31n9GWIcic0mg12hjWbU6NJ3NfWzVeiG8Stw' target='_blank'>PhD Degree Requirements for Post-Bachelor Students</a>（已拥有学士学位）/<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=BraKR4e2kFr4D09bvvvvvv2KWI7X392Yor9aJ_kOoQzOHFzG5IDYRGkT0BLYRlElbfcVdbPaR8EBfbgLf6yVFeI' target='_blank'>PhD Degree Requirements for Post-Master Students</a>（已拥有硕士学位）(PDF)</li>	<li>MA项目要求：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=3rHk7m9jk78yswTozzzzzzUS6O4amcLCspc7KRWbsilbQGlBPOtCYBW9rqECY1D1ojkyGgwYjC7djCMaWiFn' target='_blank'>MA Degree Requirements</a>(PDF)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=VrxbIdzkwhmWQkeTlAurvUfvY4VcAUGB8DV7eqFvdhhMZsG5JFMAW1ZPF61QiDzqUftBnBgFV61zFM6jJdyjpzvypYxOeCBA0AJlD1y1XDIm8GZtOb9ALR0ZUBqZrbVDEudV9A8479-1CaE4ABAsFzMR_LrApddpy' target='_blank'>Estimate of Expenses for International Students</a> Boston University</p><p>(2) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=4rjT-BDiw8gc07WdiGk8ydfwsuFSFnBfenQOYBdKOEHPPxwUofLAiNxqzbz3jrz9BR81sjae321gBkdxWWaFndxvT' target='_blank'>Graduate Program Admissions</a> Department of Physics, Boston University</p><p>(3) <a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/r