u.org/redirect?code=erlnE6yMLwBRm6-7OOOOOOgJwDTtF5Pf-VeUBPy0AGNT3YmTwv4BFjPk50NBRLBzKVAHigHl6nhlxuG8x3JF' target='_blank'>面试</a>。请在申请前查看教授列表及其研究领域。录取的PhD将会获得$30,000（2013-2014数据）奖学金，发放5年。*(3)</p><h3>营养学</h3><p>波士顿大学营养学MS学制2学期，要求申请者拥有学士学位，修读过化学、<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=6ri8verHwSnOKhPrv_lNBYBu9gP1rN-hJli8mN0E1iLYFQdadh-lqvWPr_1bb5UCf1yf6Oe2OP5wzwxH26Oe2FwgNbkAGof61ejOP5RBBz1yvedDdcEYTF6' target='_blank'>有机化学</a>、生物和生理学。没有完成先决条件课程的学生亦可申请，入学后会有专门的选课顾问帮助学生完成该项要求。申请者还要提供GRE<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=8rL6TCNxkwxMeydsllllllAwNbk7UeE3Ff6wCP1cNtDfNB1oCaZ3jnrYLB59sBgvuFMpCAMFLEMQcxMpCxqPoFqICL' target='_blank'>成绩单</a>、托福成绩单，3封推荐信、<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=xrVOpgSKw6zMHsvu444444UxRolh0mnyYKLPnJbiA2yQOmjQx5GCtU0we_6zoD6DCD6piAwtqIotoHZHvqZHvk6pVW0pVW61nVl5nVlVFwmsJOd' target='_blank'>个人陈述</a>少于500字。</p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=wrYmhljlk9aKYUP4UUUUUUZG3SMtEIz5mu1Y1YkH-RUQzFWIko8grRtLrEhveZrgxM7vSO2pF_H7MW47q3wfSHcItgLRV' target='_blank'>Graduate Programs</a>&nbsp;SAR Boston</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ZrygfZwvwlsJdPp5MMM4vvAHUu2GdY4qQ0b0b6F9bzFV8ugqd3e683Cxbh6kZEQGrigYaE5hu-vOuiYL_z-uV707bnGhvSGx1a6xo_Rw1g9YsgGh3ETm35GwohGxoEBmv6ebdUrxTKrh4wr-TKrzX0mgXwRHTY4s1YJLTwmgoYmFTKrZdlJrXvER7V0HDl6qmM' target='_blank'>Admission Requirements</a>&nbsp;MS in Human Physiology SAR Boston</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=erlnE6yQLVxrLCOd-----ddMCpAbg2K4iUaOaOpcHBpLzNx8B2qZPd80PrMxyw6VN5noMaGQ_P6H4HcHJvZ3JheSGv3K4QmUJLgjdzNqhT_8wzvuFOA_36gSKcA2A052Cb5k1-6kB-MZHb3BoeS1w1DxpNDJXN4_e0PBsHP_lCsVlhbi5lBregMr20q73GXn0GUW3gjd9EotqoVkUoPVoZad1jF' target='_blank'>Admission Requirements</a>&nbsp;PhD in Human Physiology SAR Boston</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=IrnDV7pAwVJpbZHLIaWTeAd3SAcT6LjdTVRylPCjfO3q8SMzGdJK51fTXjOtl-7Zwu1FdsjXkl-G1OGcumg2vFc-2DcVyQ1Xsx5Gob0B3Dd0kGt0f3G1HSnkc1kG7UNUqzFL79cotyoB0ddvXw9MOT6bdb7uudJPVGhhsxdpTl_lhpjdp51Gf_safyXiHzIkZf_Hn1' target='_blank'>Admission Requirements</a>&nbsp;MS in Nutrition SAR Boston</p><h3>职业疗法</h3><p>波士顿大学职业疗法系（Occupational Therapy）开设的研究生项目有全日制的职业疗法硕士学位和康复学博士学位，以及专业职业理疗博士学位远程教育项目。职业疗法硕士（Master of Science in Occupational Therapy, MSOT）要求申请者拥有本科学位，修读过人体解剖学、人体<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=dr1GqV8Twdft_1JFZZZZZZrYiWKOwq8g-a1YPz9UiQ0ai_9jPVvgx5bYFtp2FSp5TjWJ1_SvTapvV_WJ1_nJdjpJd_q' target='_blank'>生理学</a>、大体解剖学、<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=FrFYCWPWw_8kIqPbNNNNNNCjlsmDHkSy3FRUW57X2qzhRqPXs5By3TMNVTMZ0kPGQkMNmZMHQCMHiCMNVCMHQZMHVFv' target='_blank'>统计学</a>、变态<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=5rk_5oG8L3NxwKDQnnnnnnm1JbA-H9dlPZx1puNLJFeZJYN6pE0lBXcIhXQbfYw2BXcIBYD2QYwCjx89j-8sIH8sju' target='_blank'>心理学</a>和<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=nrIeztg0kiLYy51Q01HzHfCyT0Auect_N7Yzr5oz3txdHN5WrYofX4dQ-Q_V5cPtoVG_JkZEsyUP_9ghAsYUP3EYV3ZkhAR8wOUViZLmcyhj8xgRCcUg42XsGCK5OBYhsqUNI' target='_blank'>成长心理学</a>。通过职业理疗中央申请系统（Occupational Therapy Centralized Application Service, OTCAS）进行申请。</p><p><strong>申请时间</strong></p><p>该项目只接受秋季入学，申请截止时间为12月15日，招生委员会从12月中旬审查录取资格，2月初发布录取通知。</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=ir67yhMFk2CbM-mkdQ20R03g3H_Blelmn7vd78VWCXIUaF4P0PEct7F7kQU-AjZSRs8C1GkVj5nhY9Rs8jlCHRbXPgTG7I38bbHws-LUrlCrJTbzRYX8VJ4' target='_blank'><strong>申请材料</strong></a></p><ul>	<li>本科<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=CrXRF8WZLDXYcz1jr3ETI8S26y1BxWZtY3OIr6_0rvHAf0v4jSYLdiAG2La8b4QQTZBal_WRoenNqU9cEplUPh8KkUetqytbreX3zM6-Ce' target='_blank'>成绩单</a>：Official transcript(s) sent directly to OTCAS，要求本科GPA3.0以上</li>	<li>GRE成绩单：GRE阅读要求不低于153分，GRE数学要求不低于144分，GRE写作要求不低于4.5分；GRE送分编号为3028</li>	<li>一篇ESSAY：One special essay question is required separately from the OTCAS application，直接邮寄至OT办公室</li>	<li><a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=MrO2caJPwYZ8xJ1sAxnZRw1gIB8TjiU1xfKRlmxpdSd9q-RMY16feGVosaF51vfcUBRhhhnWl5j2Flg85Yx2IFBgKQNxBRfQyUkKVuwBXz' target='_blank'>推荐信</a>：Three letters of reference, to be submitted electronically or in paper form directly to OTCAS</li>	<li>先决条件课程成绩单：Official transcripts indicating completion of the six (6) prerequisite courses</li>	<li>TOEFL：写作单项不低于22分，口语单项不低于23分，阅读单项不低于25分，听力单项不低于21分</li></ul><h3>康复学</h3><p>波士顿大学康复学博士（PhD in Rehabilitation Sciences）要求申请者至少拥有康复学相关领域的学士学位，硕士学位亦可申请。接受秋季入学，招生委员会从1月15日开始审查录取资格，申请者若打算申请<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=dr1GqVpiLOJkATcvNycDXKtQedskirw-mPkO-_MUwN8ZVeBQDtLOahJP4nrx-R0c01UtI23Iyq4irHM1cP612qlc12HM1cwbQY1ONvIqx-' target='_blank'>奖学金</a>，请尽量在1月15日之前递交申请。申请者需要递交的资料包括GRE成绩单、高等教育成绩单、推荐信3和ESSAY。ESSAY中必须表述想要的导师及其原因。*(3)</p><p>外部链接：</p><ul>	<li>康复科学教员列表：<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=9rpcSXFzLo3V1tY0CCCCCeS87BOm2ytIhe7a7ad2BGmF83VTwxvY8UM_8bGwMxZbyluaq0lLo_x3-GoTRxVjRcgOCiNMZj-IpnP6Qly1CWgIn3ASqjrnCzDxRHKlPKfKT2z2jiWTjQdTyPAnCwhTtFXNDs-iVwbH1Ehs1TWtUo1YUaQrArymqE3GDtSjh' target='_blank'>Rehabilitation Sciences Faculty</a></li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=4rjT-BD1wcXfY2U2VVVVVlzCMmHIk0LUuzhNhNpZXkhX7xo_lsPDJUr2JdV9ZtTo2rvDpGEfTwP0Z6-vOui5OZZrW4prAfdJaBMeaRQ8GIB6Zw2fGXvT-H5jXoSuK4PHYJ' target='_blank'>Prerequisite Courses</a>&nbsp;MSOT SAR Boston</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=_r75g1qdLH56-eN7xBW_-CSLZTEItNzwO0g_E32GqVQThyD-1aXq9Ax0rqrzc7QYAuOtf7BU55IBwxHwBW_kGhK5vVRhMl-wOFOTyjb-lOHgfkoghUp5cyo-jqYgoKz8BirtnwiUHSKwxpwBE_sDtTyS1iJALSTTADSaooqm6QC0dAbhKmanw3_WhYaotT0_DwOHLjEcG' target='_blank'>Required Materials</a>&nbsp;MSOT SAR Boston</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_1DkbcX2zO2VS2oBWPco8yo2fM3ZKS8qAR9_Xv-SEetYPt60j55d0_qnCR0yYDUqcBX6faUPpzgFJ970Uj_kyDSFcUyVOyOwrvUwgkU_xCD_J