C%96%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>生物化学</a>（Biochemistry）专业开设的学位项目有MA、PhD以及<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/MD' target='_blank'>MD</a>/PhD。</p><p><strong>学位要求</strong></p><p>要求拥有学士学位，通常本科专业是<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>生物化学</a>、生物或<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>化学</a>，且修读过一般生物学、一般<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>化学</a>、<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E6%9C%89%E6%9C%BA%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>有机化学</a>、<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86' target='_blank'>物理</a>学、<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>物理化学</a>和微积分课程的申请者可申请<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>生物化学</a>MA或post-bachelor PhD； 已获得<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>生物化学</a>或相近领域学位的学生，可申请post-MA PhD项目。*(1)</p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=UrsQlJEKw6zMHsa3CCCCCCPVZWuwBGQgCvxBxB2XErMxBqjEN_mI1K50-LBaTYbQmUJ7EUwhxUJhYCkhfbk2sEFBHWGBDsFu2YriGKw6GIAMK' target='_blank'>MA in Biochemistry</a>&nbsp;GMS BUSM</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=0rRNYshOwp7HowBI111111cFYZBVdWEikCkCgNjOu1jDJcr-VBTnJ4Y39BTEIfu3HFaQHklpMA9oQA0pJ8rpuJ29An2YriGKw6G9qwzs' target='_blank'>PhD in Biochemistry</a>&nbsp;GMS BUSM</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>微生物学</strong></h3><p>波士顿大学<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%BE%AE%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>微生物学</a>（Microbiology）专业开设的学位项目有：</p><ul>	<li>PhD in Microbiology</li>	<li>Training Program in Pathogenesis and Host&mdash;Pathogen Interactions (HPI)</li>	<li>PhD,&nbsp;<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/MD' target='_blank'>MD</a>/PhD in Immunology Training Program, ITP</li></ul><p>ITP要求申请者拥有正规大学学士学位，有很强的生物和<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%8C%96%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>化学</a>背景，提供<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/GRE' target='_blank'>GRE</a>&nbsp;general成绩，不要求<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/GRE' target='_blank'>GRE</a>&nbsp;subject成绩。</p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=Nr20uK8jk78ysq5kZZZZZYO_MOX-yrwsP0kVkVE1swx1aMEFLqnqmZTuzd-cJ8P2R_z3CZ6UHZaUPcfoc3fq14FzhYYzTE1QqKr3S6ZbDEQTO0Q6xhREfsnF_X_edBuen_wbr9JnV4_FPwTazj_oHcJ8S3J8E3l9N_lsqejLqWenBShjueBJfnAg' target='_blank'>PhD, MD/PhD in Immunology Training</a>&nbsp;GMS BUSM</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>病理学与实验室医学</strong></h3><p>波士顿大学病理学与实验室<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E5%8C%BB%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>医学</a>（Pathology &amp; Laboratory Medicine）提供的学位项目有：</p><ul>	<li>MA in Pathology（founded in 2003）</li>	<li>PhD in Pathology &amp; Laboratory Medicine</li></ul><p>除病理学基础课程外，学生还可选择以下3个方向之一，进行学习：</p><ul>	<li>Pathology&mdash;Cell and Molecular Biology</li>	<li>Pathology&mdash;Immunology</li>	<li>Pathology&mdash;Neuroscience</li></ul><p>申请说明：除基本申请资料外，招生委员会同样看重申请者的实验室经验以及出版物或公开作品。申请者第一年是通过PiBS进入PhD项目，第二学年自动进入以上方向之一进行学习。</p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=7r_i3IzoLzABI-QDUUUBEEH8O8K93ej2udp3H8lub6k4Z71FrXL5TsKF0Pv8TsCaulviApei3pji3WviApe5o42wCAzV5Qdq3_9x3QLtX_BOK-2q5pInWAoZ5-k' target='_blank'>Pathology &amp; Laboratory Medicine</a>&nbsp;GMS BUSM</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=CrXRF8zTk1JUIYdDzWhQ3vRUGweR9Hl_0vSCQ9BEmdVftc3eXmCPgTy9zaYwFJkxpwS3NMDDlDqA_FgM9QXri3QXnZFgM9mlkbmF7aam7VPXFILXUGFa-qEHWCYRowqQ3TYwq4YxysPPwVz0' target='_blank'>PhD in Pathology &amp; Laboratory Medicine</a>&nbsp;GMS BUSM</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>药理学与实验室治疗</strong></h3><p>波士顿大学<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E8%8D%AF%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>药理学</a>与实验室治疗（Pharmacology &amp; Experimental Therapeutics）专业开设的研究生学位项目有MA、PhD与<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/MD' target='_blank'>MD</a>/PhD。NIGMS研究所主要提供的生物分子<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E8%8D%AF%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>药理学</a>培训项目（Biomolecular Pharmacology training program），以下学位项目录取的学生有机会进到以下项目：</p><ul>	<li>PhD in Pharmacology</li>	<li>PhD in Biomedical Engineering</li>	<li>PhD in Neuroscience*(1)(2)</li></ul><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=orDtO5chwkcdG5Hq66666yZ3TC9NPaDMiSiSm8fSH8AIoxcXn-z9kSh4gV9yDqxALB3JRBiJzBitLB3JRZjt3v9t2vx-g_IOLGp2O5p2nDYWn0kmLR6P7gxl7DNpL0jmL3qpXV' target='_blank'>Pharmacology &amp; Experimental Therapeutics</a>&nbsp;GMS BUSM</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=4rjT-BYTk1JUIs5kZZZZZZ5_MOX-yrwsQSyryrb3XaA4znNCDzHw-ODpYQaDbevXlehXSQ2mK_H-KYfAFo9Q' target='_blank'>NIGMS Program in Biomolecular Pharmacology</a>&nbsp;GMS BUSM</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3><strong>生理学与生物物理学</strong></h3><p>波士顿大学<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%94%9F%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>生理学</a>与<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%94%9F%E7%89%A9%E7%89%A9%E7%90%86' target='_blank'>生物物理</a>学（Physiology &amp; Biophysics）提供的学位类型有MA、PhD和<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/MD' target='_blank'>MD</a>/PhD。</p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=orDtO5cewqQ5MjnGiiiiihGTaHR0cDovFtyXyXN4mj2hNMrX-I29XJgPsaS9NVxwkrZg6-4kriI7Zasoa7FYPcrzP4mGEqIBFNy2h8CrXl2-KezfsA7sA3d8X1' target='_blank'>Physiology &amp; Biophysics</a>&nbsp;GMS BUSM</p><p>&nbsp;</p><h3>神经科学</h3><p><strong>基本信息：</strong></p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:14.76%">			<p>开设学位</p>			</td>			<td style="width:14.76%">			<p>MA、PhD</p>			</td>			<td style="width:14.76%">			<p>学费</p>			</td>			<td style="width:21.46%">			<p>$52,816</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.44%">			<p>申请截止日期</p>			</td>			<td style="width:15.84%">			<p>12月15日</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:14.76%">			<p>TOEFL要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:14.76%">			<p>90-100</p>			</td>			<td style="width:14.76%">			<p>GPA要求</p>			</td>			<td style="width:21.46%">			<p>3.0</p>			</td>			<td style="width:18.44%">			<p>可申请学期<