lank'>医学</a>（Pediatric Dentistry）</p><p>&bull; 牙周病学（Periodontology）</p><p>&bull; 假牙修复学（Prosthodontics）*(1)</p><p>注：CAGS即Certificate of Advanced Graduate Study，研修所进行证明。</p><p><strong>学位要求</strong></p><ul>	<li>DMD要求申请者必须在美国或加拿大已获得4年制学士学位。*(2)</li>	<li>Advanced Standing DMD要求申请者已获得美国或加拿大之外国家等同于DMD的<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%89%99%E5%8C%BB%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>牙医学</a>学位。*(3)</li>	<li>BA/DMD是7年制的学位项目，前三年在艺术与科学学院就读，后四年在<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%89%99%E5%8C%BB%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>牙医学</a>院就读。*(4)</li></ul><p>联系方式：</p><p>DMD Program Applicants:&nbsp;<a href='mailto:applyDMD@bu.edu' target='_blank'>applyDMD@bu.edu</a></p><p>Advanced Standing:&nbsp;<a href='mailto:asdent@bu.edu' target='_blank'>asdent@bu.edu</a></p><p>Post-doctoral:&nbsp;<a href='mailto:postadm@bu.edu' target='_blank'>postadm@bu.edu</a>&nbsp;*(5)</p><p>参考资料：</p><p>(1)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=1rdft_3BLpMoTcmq7uX2P5aGgGZfebotjNL8ZESj-fhR94LHjSGN94Q2hZrFcDreBAu-fuwG30L0wyvzgt1Xewa5K1tHdvqy4L' target='_blank'>Programs</a>&nbsp;SDM, Boston</p><p>(2)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=qrTydPtnwmHu4c459eef8ZFrsJvb_chdk-GviYlnOo7qj5du9dqYVITuvnfOMwabYvhOor4UFzwMdvwiJrOandO6p170rXFQf1' target='_blank'>Requirements for DMD</a>&nbsp;SDM, Boston</p><p>(3)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=nrIezt2QLVxrL0S94mYENermgCBiXF_aKmvonq5grkrcVTUptr2xrZR4oAqRqMx2afIahOC1-bZvhv9B3ewlQag29MnoUKhWL' target='_blank'>Requirements for AS</a>&nbsp;Advanced Standing DMD SDM, Boston</p><p>(4)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=qrTydPtXwF1Egm7XDDDMpppECaAX95RmHqrqrLxYroxj1ahmFZtD1fyKCZt4Hqts7oM_d9M_l9MIK9L_41P1j7Y0x1ZILHPJL7vrLFZXm' target='_blank'>Baccalaureate/DMD (Seven-Year Program)</a>&nbsp;SDM, Boston</p><p>(5)&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" href='http://www.qianmu.org/redirect?code=erlnE6BnkkP-GMK2xxxxxxVG3SMtEIz5UAlRlR4pxKgX4AtBDM-iNvKSN6WbbO7RfcpwZjMnx2SQaiZh1X' target='_blank'>Contact</a>&nbsp;SDM Admission, Boston</p><h2><strong>神学院</strong></h2><p>波士顿大学<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%A5%9E%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>神学</a>院（School of Theology, STH）成立于1839年，研究生开设7个学位项目：</p><table border="1" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0">	<tbody>		<tr>			<td style="width:109px">			<p>项目</p>			</td>			<td style="width:248px">			<p>项目英文</p>			</td>			<td style="width:157px">			<p>学位类型</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:109px">			<p><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%A5%9E%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>神学</a>硕士</p>			</td>			<td style="width:248px">			<p>Master of Divinity Degree</p>			</td>			<td style="width:157px">			<p>MDiv</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:109px">			<p><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%A5%9E%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>神学</a>研究硕士</p>			</td>			<td style="width:248px">			<p>Master of Theological Studies Degree</p>			</td>			<td style="width:157px">			<p>MTS、PhD</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:109px">			<p>宗教<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90' target='_blank'>音乐</a>硕士</p>			</td>			<td style="width:248px">			<p>Master of Sacred Music Degree</p>			</td>			<td style="width:157px">			<p>MSM</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:109px">			<p>圣教硕士</p>			</td>			<td style="width:248px">			<p>Master of Sacred Theology Degree</p>			</td>			<td style="width:157px">			<p>STM</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:109px">			<p>教牧学博士</p>			</td>			<td style="width:248px">			<p>Doctor of Ministry Degree</p>			</td>			<td style="width:157px">			<p>DMin</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:109px">			<p><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%A5%9E%E5%AD%A6' target='_blank'>神学</a>与宗教<a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E9%9F%B3%E4%B9%90' target='_blank'>音乐</a>硕士</p>			</td>			<td style="width:248px">			<p>Master of Divinity &amp; Master of Sacred Music</p>			</td>			<td style="width:157px">			<p>MDiv/MSM</p>			</td>		</tr>		<tr>			<td style="width:109px">			<p><a href='http://www.qianmu.org/%E7%A5%9E%E5%AD%A